186
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,673
Sim, o que?

187
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,199
O que?

188
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:13,637
Diga-lhes para esperar.
Diga-lhes para esperar.Esperar

189
