657
00:52:43,880 --> 00:52:45,632
- Enfrentar um dragão.

658
00:52:49,760 --> 00:52:52,115
Amor juvenil.

659
00:52:52,840 --> 00:52:54,034
Quão...

660
00:52:56,400 --> 00:52:57,628
Comovente.

